<!DOCTYPE html>
html(lang="en")
  head
    meta(charset="UTF-8")
    meta(name="viewport", content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0")
    link(rel="stylesheet", href="style.css")
    link(rel="stylesheet", href="https://cdn-ftfish.rhcloud.com/redactedjs/css/redacted-script-bold.css")

body.app
  title Card Interaction

  .workspace
    h1.intro Card Interaction
      small `click` to expand card

    .wall
      each $, i in Array(4)
        .tileGroup
          each $$, j in Array(4)
            article.tile
              .article__cover(style=`background-image: url(//images.weserv.nl/?url=unsplash.it/200/300?image=${i * 20 + j * 5 + 20}&il)`)
              .article__info
                h3.article__title article title
                p.article__desc Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Neque pariatur facilis epellendus saepe, illo deserunt nesciunt.

  blockquote.info
    | inspired from 
    a(href="https://dribbble.com/shots/1908087-Card-Interaction") Card Interaction
    |  by 
    a(href="https://dribbble.com/JonathanHowell") Jonathan Howell
